response.original_title: 容祖儿 Another Side Joey My Secret Live 演唱会
response.overview: From July 13 to August 27 in 2023, C-pop diva Joey Yung held 34 shows of her ANOTHER SIDE …… JOEY•MY SECRET•LIVE at the Hong Kong Academy for Performing Arts. Marking her second side-track concert, ANOTHER SIDE captures Joey's performances of her well-known B-sides, including "Melting," "The Girl Who Wishes To See The Morning Light," "Playing Puzzle Alone," "Please Stay," " Can't Defend From A Heart Stealer," "13 o'clock," Honey!, "Little Day," "Gone With The Flare," "No One Knows Gemini" and more.
response.title: 容祖儿 Another Side Joey My Secret Live 演唱会
